    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly in incredible shape and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and staying on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without that brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
